snippet: Former Italy boss Cesare Prandelli has resigned as Valencia coach after one win in eight La Liga matches in charge, the Spanish team said on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Former Italy boss Cesare Prandelli has resigned as Valencia coach after one win in eight La Liga matches in charge, the Spanish team said on Friday.

headline.main: Prandelli Quits Valencia After Woeful Run
headline.print_headline: Prandelli Quits Valencia After Woeful Run
